# Remove Trial System & Fix Splash Screen Crash

The app crashes on splash screen because [getAppStatus()](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#556-595) checks trial data (`edux_has_selected_package`, `edux_trial_data_v2`) which may be missing or corrupted for existing installs. Since trials are no longer used, we remove the entire trial system and simplify the license flow to: **Setup → Request License → Licensed → Login/Dashboard**.

## Proposed Changes

### LicenseService

#### [MODIFY] [license_service.dart](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart)

- **Remove** [TrialData](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#124-226) class (lines 124–225)
- **Remove** `AppLicenseStatus.trial` and `AppLicenseStatus.noPackageSelected` enum values
- **Remove** trial methods: [startTrialWithPackage](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#312-384), [startFreeTrial](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#385-405), [selectPackageDirectly](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#406-418), [getTrialData](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#419-448), [clearTrialData](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#449-457), [shouldInvalidateTrial](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#1210-1225), [getTrialTimeRemaining](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#613-631), [isFreeTrial](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#632-637), [getFreeTrialStudentLimit](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#638-643), [hasSelectedPackage](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#296-305), [markPackageAsSelected](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#306-311), [getSelectedPackageId](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#1226-1231)
- **Simplify [getAppStatus()](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#556-595)**: Check license → pending → expired (no trial/package checks)
- **Simplify [isModuleAccessible()](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#596-612)**: Only check licensed status
- **Remove** [registerSchoolInFirestoreWithPackage](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#752-809) (trial-specific registration)

---

### Splash Screen

#### [MODIFY] [splash_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/features/splash/splash_screen.dart)

Simplified flow:
1. Check [isSchoolSetup()](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/database/app_database.dart#425-430) → go to setup if not
2. Check [getAppStatus()](file:///c:/Users/asims/Downloads/Development/EDU_X/lib/services/license_service.dart#556-595) → if `licensed`, go to login; otherwise go to `requestLicense`
3. Remove all trial invalidation, package selection checks, and trial status routing

