## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `flutter build windows` — Ensures the app compiles without errors after all changes

### Manual Verification
1. Launch the app fresh (delete any existing DB/prefs)
2. Confirm splash → setup wizard → request license (no package selection step)
3. With an existing licensed install, confirm splash → login screen
4. Confirm dashboard loads without trial banner
